\lim _{h \rightarrow 0} \frac{(x \cdot|x|)+h-(x \cdot|x|)}{h} \\ =\lim _{h \rightarrow 0} \frac{h}{h}=1\end{array}
$$ $$
So f(x) \text { is differentiable }
